longBusinessSummary: Joyas International Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, primarily engages in financing business in the People's Republic of China and Europe. Joyas International Holdings Limited was incorporated in 2006 and is headquartered in Causeway Bay, Hong Kong. Joyas International Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Joyas Investment Group Limited.
